title: MisterMusic Show 412 - indie, alternative, rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 412 - 192kbps MP3  [120 min]


New music this week from Red Hot Chili Peppers, Wye Oak, and Palace Winter.
The Oldie of the Week was number 1 in America during Mid-May of 1977. It is the only number 1 hit on the Billboard Hot 100 chart by this band, even though the album is considered by many the best album of the 70s.

Plus the usual mix of over 5 decades of indie, alternative and classic hits.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

For recorded podcasts of the MisterMusic show, visit his podcast page-  
http://mistermusicshow.com/ . Shows are updated there first every Sunday.
Or you can google search mistermusicshow (spelled as one word) and you'll find it.
